text: Click here for SBI Associate Banks Chief Medical Officer in SBI Associate Banks Final Results SBI Results 2015 – PO Main Exam Results: State Bank of India (SBI) has released main examination results for the post of Probationary Officer. Preliminary Examination (Phase-I) was held on 20, 21, 27 & 28-06-2015, Main examination was held on 26-07-2015. Selected candidates have to attend for Phase-III (Group Discussion and Interview) from 07-09-2015. Candidates may download their call letter from 28-08-2015. Appeared candidates can check their result at below link… Click here for PO Main Exam Results SBI Results 2015 – Manager & Asst Manager in SBI Associate Banks Online Test Results Out: State Bank of India (SBI) has released online test results for the post of Manager (Chartered Accountant) & Assistant Manager (Chartered Accountant) in SBI Associate Banks.
